CASE 
  WHEN school_degree = "no high school (secondary school)" THEN "A. No high school (secondary school)"
  WHEN school_degree =  "some high school" THEN "B. Some high school"
  WHEN school_degree = "high school diploma or equivalent (GED)" THEN "C. High school diploma or equivalent (GED)"
  WHEN school_degree = "associate's degree" THEN "D. Associate's degree"
  WHEN school_degree = "some college credit, no degree" THEN "E. Some college credit, no degree"
  WHEN school_degree = "bachelor's degree" THEN "F. Bachelor's degree"
  WHEN school_degree = "trade, technical, or vocational training" THEN "G. Trade, technical, or vocational training"
  WHEN school_degree = "master's degree (non-professional)" THEN "H. Master's degree (non-professional)"
  WHEN school_degree = "Ph.D." THEN "I. Ph.D."
  WHEN school_degree = "professional degree (MBA, MD, JD, etc.)" THEN "J. Professional degree (MBA, MD, JD, etc.)"
END
CASE WHEN is_first_dev_job = 0 THEN 'No' WHEN is_first_dev_job = 1 THEN 'Yes' END
CASE WHEN job_relocate = 0 THEN 'No: Not Willing to' WHEN job_relocate = 1 THEN 'Yes: Willing To' END
CASE WHEN is_ethnic_minority = 0 THEN 'No, not an ethnic minority' WHEN is_ethnic_minority = 1 THEN 'Yes, an ethnic minority' END
CASE WHEN is_software_dev = 0 THEN 'Aspiring Developer' WHEN is_software_dev = 1 THEN 'Current Developer' END
CASE WHEN bootcamp_attend = 0 THEN 'No, did not attend' WHEN bootcamp_attend = 1 THEN 'Yes, did attend' END
